author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
Today, I'm ignoring the big budget videos and the well-known bands and looking at some of the lesser known, the unsigned, the new or just the dedicated. Thanks to all the musicians who have been sending in videos - many more arrived after I'd recorded this - I will watch, we will reply and we will cover more, so keep them coming. 
The email address to send them to is on the home page.
Links to all of the videos featured here will follow later tonight.....so please check back. 
**Please note - we're not monetising this video - any revenue from ads will go to the bands featured** 

To come and see Justin Hawkins Rides Again LIVE across the UK, find tickets here: 
https://www.aegpresents.co.uk/event/justin-hawkins-rides-again/

title: How Interested Are You In The Unknown?
